c: 2
v: 251
t: "Naizvozvo vakave vanovakunda nekuda kwaAllah, uye Dawood (Dhavhidha) akauraya Jaaloot (Goriyati), uye Allah vakamupa humambo (mushure mekufa kwaTaaloot (Sauro)) nehungwaru (huporofita), uye vakamudzidzisa zvavaida. Uye dai Allah vasina kuisa boka revanhu pamusoro perimwe, zvirokwazvo, nyika ingadai yakazara nezvisakarurama. Asi Allah vazere nemakomborero kuzvinhu zvese zvinorarama"